<ab>
<lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">θα</supplied><unclear>υ</unclear>μάσιον κεκράτηκέ σε φιλέφηβον σθε
<lb n="2" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">ν </supplied><gap reason="lost" atLeast="2" atMost="3" unit="character"/>ων Ἀλκείδης καὶ ταχὺς Ἑρμῆς
<lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" atLeast="2" atMost="3" unit="character"/> στάδιον κεκόπωκέ σε φιλάεθλ' ὡς
<lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" atLeast="2" atMost="3" unit="character"/><unclear>ε</unclear>νος Πολυδεύκης ποτε καὶ <app type="editorial"><lem><choice><reg>Πηλεὺς</reg><orig>Πευσευς</orig></choice></lem><rdg resp="J. Bingen, cf. ed.pr. comm. line 4"><choice><reg>Καινέυς</reg><orig>Καινευσευς</orig></choice></rdg></app>
<lb n="5" xml:id="lb5"/><gap reason="lost" atLeast="2" atMost="3" unit="character"/><app type="editorial"><lem><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>εσιαις</lem><rdg resp="H. Maehler"><unclear>ν</unclear>εσιαις</rdg></app> πεπλά<unclear>ν</unclear>ηκέ σε τοῖς Ἀγρίοις
<lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" atLeast="2" atMost="3" unit="character"/>θαι Μελέαγρος <unclear>σ</unclear>οβαρός, Ἄδωνις
<lb n="7"/><gap reason="lost" atLeast="3" atMost="4" unit="character"/> <unclear>π</unclear>εποθημένε <choice><reg>σύγγαμε</reg><orig>σύνγαμε</orig></choice>, κῦμα λάβρον
<lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">πόντ</supplied><unclear>ο</unclear>υ πεφοβήσαι, μένε, λίτομαι <choice><reg>κινδυν-</reg><orig>κινδ<hi rend="superscript">υ</hi></orig></choice>
<lb n="9"/><gap reason="lost" atLeast="3" atMost="4" unit="character"/><unclear>σ</unclear>αι <space atLeast="2" atMost="3" unit="character"/> καὶ <app type="editorial"><lem>στέξον</lem><rdg resp="H. Maehler, cf. ed.pr. comm. line 9">στεῖξον</rdg></app> βραχὺ <add place="above">λι</add>τανεύω παρά
<lb n="10"/><app type="editorial"><lem resp="PN J. Bromberg (from photo)"><gap reason="lost" atLeast="4" atMost="5" unit="character"/><unclear>μ</unclear>ολως</lem><rdg><gap reason="lost" atLeast="4" atMost="5" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ολως</rdg></app> σοι, φίλτατε, λύπην ἔκβαλε σῆς
<lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ψυχῆς </supplied> και<unclear>ρ</unclear>ὸς γὰρ καλὸς αὔριον ἔσται τὰ καλὰ πρ<hi rend="superscript">ο</hi>
<lb n="12" break="no"/><gap reason="lost" atLeast="4" atMost="5" unit="character"/>τας, ἆ γαμέτα <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
<lb n="13"/><gap reason="lost" atLeast="5" atMost="6" unit="character"/><app type="editorial"><lem><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>η δοῦναι</lem><rdg resp="J. Bromberg (from photo)"><unclear>μ</unclear>η δοῦναι</rdg></app> βραχεῖαν συνφοραῖς εὐψυχίαν <del rend="erasure">παρὰ ψυχήν</del>

